{
  "id": "adv_event_2209_01_02",
  "title": "未来とつながるマジカルメロディ 2話 ミクの記念日",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "初めまして、初音ミクです",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEのみんな、よろしくね",
      "startTime": 3.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "凄い……これ、ホログラムって技術ですか？",
      "startTime": 7.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、顔合わせが出来てる……",
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私からも、みんなのこと、ちゃんと見えてるよ",
      "startTime": 14.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "天動瑠依ちゃん、鈴村優ちゃん、奥山すみれちゃん",
      "startTime": 19.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うっ！　本物のミクちゃんから名前呼ばれた……",
      "startTime": 25.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "うち、幸せ者過ぎるやろ～……",
      "startTime": 29.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こちらこそ初めまして、ミクちゃん！",
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、凄い機械だね",
      "startTime": 36.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "普段、初音さんがライブステージに立つ時も",
      "startTime": 39.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "同じような原理の機械を使ってるそうだよ",
      "startTime": 42.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん",
      "startTime": 45.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku003.m4a",
      "text": "呼ぶ時はミクでいいよ",
      "startTime": 47.3417031606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか。分かった",
      "startTime": 50.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私はネットワークの世界に生きてるからね",
      "startTime": 52.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku004.m4a",
      "text": "いろんなデバイスを、自由に行き来出来るんだ",
      "startTime": 57.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だから、バーチャル・シンガーっていうんだ",
      "startTime": 61.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……やっぱり触れられないのね",
      "startTime": 64.3131266911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あくまでも投影されてる状態やからなぁ",
      "startTime": 67.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、こうしてお話し出来るだけでも十分やんか",
      "startTime": 71.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "歌を届けるのに、必ずしも体は必要じゃないからね",
      "startTime": 75.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku005.m4a",
      "text": "今のままでも、出来ることは沢山あるんだよ",
      "startTime": 81.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なるほど、そうかもしれないわね",
      "startTime": 85.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……改めてよろしくね、ミク",
      "startTime": 88.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さて。この前も伝えたけど、トリエルの三人には",
      "startTime": 91.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "マジカルミライに出演してもらう",
      "startTime": 94.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ミクちゃんのライブに出演かぁ",
      "startTime": 97.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと観る側やったから、嬉しいし感慨深いわぁ",
      "startTime": 100.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "改めて、出演を決めてくれてありがとう！",
      "startTime": 105.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが出演してくれたら、絶対素敵なライブになるよ",
      "startTime": 109.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ミクちゃんからのオファーだもん、断れないよ！",
      "startTime": 114.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "お祝いの気持ち、いーっぱい届けるね",
      "startTime": 118.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "曲構成はどうするん？　うちらの既存曲を",
      "startTime": 121.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ歌うだけなんは、なんや申し訳ないなぁ",
      "startTime": 125.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ミクの曲をカバーしたり、でしょうか？",
      "startTime": 129.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、対応は可能ですけど……",
      "startTime": 133.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いや、今回は新曲をつくろうと思ってるんだ",
      "startTime": 136.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ミクの記念日をお祝いする楽曲の予定だ",
      "startTime": 139.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ほんまに！？　めっちゃ嬉しいわぁ",
      "startTime": 142.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "8月31日といえばミクちゃんの記念日やもんなぁ！",
      "startTime": 145.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "確かに私達、お祝いの曲ってやったことなかったね",
      "startTime": 150.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "イベントにもピッタリだし、楽しみ！",
      "startTime": 156.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そして、もう一つ……",
      "startTime": 159.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "新曲の作詞は、三人に任せたい",
      "startTime": 161.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私達が作詞を……ですか？",
      "startTime": 164.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ああ。想いを込めて、自分達で書いてもらいたい",
      "startTime": 168.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくの機会だ。挑戦してみてもいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 173.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一理あるなぁ",
      "startTime": 177.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
